When he will get a connection back, he will be able to synchronize its local database with the common centralized database.</td></tr><tr class="row-1"><td class="category">Additional Information</td><td colspan="5">When designing this feature, a great care should be taken that the local database stored on the user's computer is encrypted and cannot be read.<br />
